        MongoDB[🗄️ MongoDB<br/>Posts + Users]
    end
    
    Browser -->|HTTP/HTTPS| React
    React -->|Axios API Calls| Express
    Express -->|Read/Write| MongoDB
    Express -->|Cache Check| Redis
    Redis -.->|Cache Miss| MongoDB
    MongoDB -.->|Update Cache| Redis
    
    style Browser fill:#FFD700
    style React fill:#61DAFB
    style Express fill:#339933,color:#fff
    style Redis fill:#DC382D,color:#fff
    style MongoDB fill:#47A248,color:#fff
```

## 🛠️ Stack Tecnológico

```
Frontend          Backend           Data              DevOps
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
React 18          Node.js 21        MongoDB 7.0       Docker
TypeScript 5      Express.js        Redis 7.0         Kubernetes
Vite              Mongoose                            Nginx Ingress
Tailwind CSS      JWT + bcrypt                        Swagger UI
shadcn/ui         Swagger JSDoc
React Router
Axios
Jest              Jest + Supertest
```

### Tecnologías Clave

- **Frontend**: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS
- **Backend**: Node.js 21 + Express + Mongoose + Redis
- **Database**: MongoDB 7.0 (base de datos) + Redis 7.0 (caché)
- **DevOps**: Docker + Kubernetes + Nginx + Multi-arch builds
- **API Docs**: Swagger UI + OpenAPI 3.0
- **Testing**: Jest + React Testing Library + Supertest

